<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>As far as compareing this item to a Treeweave...don't.  Most people on planes and dragon runs take off their Treeweaves (and other high AC armor) and wear Dwarven Ringmail Tunics instead (AC:12 SvMagic,Fire,Cold+8 cost:20pp).  Why give up all that AC for a few Saves?, Well, if you have to ask, you haven't been to the planes or on a dragon run.  The combination of SvMagic, SvFire, +20Str make this item highly valuable.  This item's extream rareity make it worth a mint.  I've never seen one of these for sale or trade, but I would guess that when it is traded, it is traded for other dragon loot or high end Kunark items.  Thanks for listening=)</font></td></tr></table>
